SUMMARY:Singles Wine and Cheese Pairing Experience
DESCRIPTION:Sips & Sparks – SINGLES Wine & Cheese Pairing Experience  in Davis\n Sunday\, May 17 | 12–3pm\nLooking to meet new people in a fun\, relaxed setting? Skip the swiping and join us at Great Bear Vineyards for an afternoon of wine\, cheese\, conversation\, and connection. \nIndulge your senses (and maybe hand out your phone number ) during this special Singles Wine & Cheese Pairing Experience\, featuring a curated flight of four award-winning wines paired with premium artisan cheeses designed to bring out the best in every bite and sip.\nThe Dates Not Apps team will be onsite helping spark genuine connections through light facilitation\, shared interests\, and easy conversation starters—so you can mingle naturally without the pressure.\n Ticket Includes: Flight of 4 Wines Paired Artisan Cheese Tasting\n Whether you’re:• A single looking to meet someone new• A foodie who loves delicious pairings• A wine enthusiast eager to explore flavor combinations• Or simply in the mood for a fun Sunday outing…\n…this experience is for you!\n What to Expect: MeetCute facilitators helping guests connect naturally Handcrafted wines paired to perfection Fun insights into wine & cheese harmony Relaxed vineyard atmosphere perfect for mingling\nSettle into a shady spot\, sip something delicious\, and enjoy an afternoon designed to help great conversations flow as easily as the wine. Additional wine and snacks will be available for purchase if you’d like to linger a little longer.\n Dietary Restrictions & PreferencesIf you have dietary restrictions or preferences\, please email us at:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com\nPlease include:• Dietary restrictions/preferences(Gluten Free\, Vegan\, Vegetarian\, Nut Free\, Pescatarian\, Shellfish Free\, etc.)• Preferred pronouns• Preferred age range:21–28 | 28–46 | 47–64 | 64+\n Great wine. Great cheese. Great company. You never know who you’ll meet at the vineyard.
URL:https://visitdavis.org/event/singles-wine-and-cheese-pairing-experience/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards 24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitdavis.org/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled-zK0eUQ.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
